        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="industry-icon public-sector-icon"></div>
          <h2>Public Sector</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Enhancing public services through effective program management and resource allocation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Public service improvement initiatives</li>
