      </div>
      <div class="industry-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="industry-icon education-icon"></div>
          <h2>Higher Education</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Supporting educational institutions with innovative solutions for improved learning outcomes.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Curriculum development enhancements</li>
